result_data.course_description: This course will explain in non-mathematical terms how essentially all biological properties are determined by the microscopic chemical properties of proteins. It will also explain how research results, especially those of structural biology, are presented to its various audiences.
important_notes: Permission Needed From Instructor
Freshman Seminar
Natural Science & Math Sector
